name: Mammoth evolution
description:
A mammoth is any species of the extinct Elephantid genus Mammuthus, one of the many genera that make up the order of trunked mammals called proboscideans.  but mammoths in other galaxies are shaped with sophistication into robot mammoths.

sci-fi movement conceptually. Inspiration by sci-fi 80s vibes like bruce pennington, Moebius (Jean Giraud)  H.R GIGER And many more.

Illustrated by ink digital 
2022
